2:27:12,051 --> 2:27:15,316
It's between my do
you know Umanath,...

1398
2:27:15,387 --> 2:27:18,720
... a hundred times richer
than you, his daughter.

1399
2:27:19,692 --> 2:27:21,990
Don't definitely come for marriage.

1400
2:27:22,695 --> 2:27:24,993
It's a minister's home wedding.
They won't let you in.

1401
2:27:25,531 --> 2:27:27,499
You know the date of marriage?.

1402
2:27:27,566 --> 2:27:29,500
Remember your promise in
front of all the villagers,'

1403
2:27:29,568 --> 2:27:31,502
' In the next auspicious date...

1404
2:27:31,570 --> 2:27:33,504
... I'll conduct the
marriage of my two daughters.

1405
2:27:33,572 --> 2:27:35,506
If it does not happen,
it means that Padayappa's...

1406
2:27:35,574 --> 2:27:38,737
... breath has stopped'.
That same day,

1407
2:27:44,383 --> 2:27:47,682
Remember, when you
stopped my marriage.

1408
2:27:47,753 --> 2:27:52,690
My dad also bowed his head like
this, thinking of his daughter.

1409
2:27:54,727 --> 2:27:56,695
As my father hanged himself...

1410
2:27:56,762 --> 2:27:59,697
... when he could not
keep up his promise,...

1411
2:28:00,733 --> 2:28:05,693
... you should also hang
yourself in shame...

1412
2:28:05,771 --> 2:28:08,706
... in front of the villagers.

1413
2:28:10,075 --> 2:28:12,373
Seeing that, I should feel happy.

1414
2:28:13,412 --> 2:28:16,381
Only then, my father's
soul will rest in peace.

1415
2:28:18,417 --> 2:28:22,376
As I suffered for not
getting the one I loved,...

1416
2:28:23,422 --> 2:28:30,385
Similarly, your daughter too
should suffer all her life.

1417
2:28:31,430 --> 2:28:38,393
My servant who is your
wife now, should cry...

1418
2:28:38,470 --> 2:28:43,066
... over her daughter's
plight, all her life.

1419
2:28:44,443 --> 2:28:48,812
That's the pleasure
Neelambari will derive...

1420
2:28:48,881 --> 2:28:52,817
... after 1 8 years of
self-imposed exile.

1421
2:28:56,121 --> 2:29:02,082
You boast that your path
is unique, don't you?.

1422
2:29:02,161 --> 2:29:05,096
My path too is unique!

1423
2:29:06,131 --> 2:29:09,430
You can't outsmart me, anymore!

1424
2:29:10,135 --> 2:29:12,763
Bravo! That was a
master plan indeed.

1425
2:29:13,138 --> 2:29:17,097
