successful politician.

1426
2:29:25,150 --> 2:29:28,119
This is the first time
it has slipped, isn't it?.

1427
2:29:30,823 --> 2:29:33,792
I change towels often
but I don't lose them.

1428
2:29:35,160 --> 2:29:37,128
You keep it safely too!

1429
2:29:38,163 --> 2:29:40,791
Do you think I've
forgotten the past?.

1430
2:29:41,500 --> 2:29:43,627
A politician may fail
to keep promises...

1431
2:29:43,702 --> 2:29:45,863
... but he will never
fail to avenge his insult.

1432
2:29:47,172 --> 2:29:50,471
Open the door,
Padayappa is leaving.

1433
2:30:25,878 --> 2:30:32,841
I'm your daughter,
I surely won't get cheated.

1434
2:30:33,552 --> 2:30:35,679
Why haven't you returned yet?.
What took you so long?.

1435
2:30:35,754 --> 2:30:37,688
Did you call for us urgently?.
What's the matter?.

1436
2:30:41,894 --> 2:30:44,863
Ask Vasundara to make
arrangements for the marriage.

1437
2:30:44,963 --> 2:30:46,931
Are you sure?.

1438
2:30:47,232 --> 2:30:50,861
- Don't you know my nature?.
- But everything is in their favour.

1439
2:30:53,572 --> 2:30:56,700
But God is in our favour!

1440
2:31:17,930 --> 2:31:19,898
Padayappa and his men may
come in disguise, be careful.

1441
2:31:20,265 --> 2:31:22,233
Don't worry, I'll take care!

1442
2:31:24,770 --> 2:31:26,897
Did you check the kitchen?.
Are they keeping a watching?.

1443
2:31:27,606 --> 2:31:29,574
Are the Mufty cops indoors?.

1444
2:32:25,998 --> 2:32:27,966
Padayappa has arrived!

1445
2:32:58,030 --> 2:32:59,998
You aren't permitted to go inside.

1446
2:33:01,700 --> 2:33:04,328
- Why?.
- Do you have an invitation?.

1447
2:33:04,870 --> 2:33:07,668
That's irrelevant!
Drive him away!

1448
2:33:07,873 --> 2:33:11,001
- He's uninvited!
- That's right!

1449
2:33:11,376 --> 2:33:13,344
In fact I've come to invite!

1450
2:33:13,545 --> 2:33:15,513
- Whom?.
- Son-in-law!

1451
2:33:16,381 --> 2:33:18,349
My son-in-law!

1452
2:33:18,717 --> 2:33:20,685
But why do you want to take him?.

1453
2:33:20,752 --> 2:33:22,344
Because this marriage
is against his wishes.

1454
2:33:22,721 --> 2:33:24,848
- Who said so?.
- The groom himself said so.

1455
2:33:25,057 --> 2:33:30,689
- My son!?. - Yes, Honourable
Minister's only son.

1456
2:33:31,730 --> 2:33:33,857
Why are you silent?.
Speak up!

1457
2:33:35,400 --> 2:33:39,029
- I'll tell you.
- Hey! Who are you?.

1458
2:33:39,738 --> 2:33:42,036
Why have you abducted me?.
Don't you know who I am?.

1459
2:33:42,908 --> 2:33:47,106
We know you, but you should know
of one man who's very popular.

1460
2:33:47,913 --> 2:33:49,881
Look there!

1461
2:33:55,921 --> 2:33:57,889
Are you trying to threaten me?.

1462
2:33:58,423 --> 2:34:00,891
- My father has many henchmen.
- They aren't henchmen.

1463
2:34:01,426 --> 2:34:03,394
They are my friends!

1464
2:34:03,595 --> 2:34:07,725
I too have a gang of
men who obey my orders.

1465
2:34:07,799 --> 2:34:12,395
Your father's henchmen are cowards.
But my men are brave.

1466
2:34:12,771 --> 2:34:15,740
But I've never misused their
services for my selfish motive.

1467
2:34:16,775 --> 2:34:20,074
I'm good to those who are good to me.
And you too are good.

1468
2:34:20,445 --> 2:34:22,413
I know that.
Tell me the truth.

1469
2:34:22,481 --> 2:34:24,415
- Weren't you involved with my daughter?.
- No!

1470
2:34:24,516 --> 2:34:27,076
- Didn't you love her?.
- No!

1471
2:34:27,185 --> 2:34:29,153
- Didn't you promise to marry her?.
- No!

1472
2:34:29,788 --> 2:34:32,086
- Didn't you love her?.
- No! Not at all!

1473
2:34:32,457 --> 2:34:34,425
Your daughter isn't worthy of me.

1474
2:34:37,963 --> 2:34:40,932
Why have you stopped?.
Face her boldly...

1475
2:34:40,999 --> 2:34:43,934
... and repeat what
you just told me.

1476
2:35:04,222 --> 2:35:06,190
Pardon me, uncle!

1477
2:35:06,825 --> 2:35:10,192
They asked me to pretend to love
Anitha, but I loved her truly.

1478
2:35:10,829 --> 2:35:14,196
If my father and Neelambari
know of this, they'll kill me.

1479
2:35:15,500 --> 2:35:17,468
You should help us unite!

1480
2:35:21,840 --> 2:35:23,808
It slips only once!

1481
2:35:27,179 --> 2:35:29,204
Father!

1482
2:35:37,522 --> 2:35:39,490
Finally you joined
him to stage a drama.

1483
2:35:40,025 --> 2:35:42,994
No. One hit, not even one hit
should fall on my son-in-law.

1484
2:35:44,529 --> 2:35:47,157
Mr.Suryaprakash,
care for your son's life.

1485
2:35:47,866 --> 2:35:49,993
Don't listen to others to
make his life miserable.

1486
2:35:50,202 --> 2:35:53,000
You are in a responsible post.
Don't misuse it.

1487
2:35:53,538 --> 2:35:55,506
Don't spoil the name of your party.

1488
2:35:55,874 --> 2:35:59,002
Enough of your advice.
He is my son. I'll compel him to marry.

1489
2:35:59,211 --> 2:36:01,179
If something happens
to my son-in-law,...

1490
2:36:01,246 --> 2:36:03,180
... then anything might happen here.

1491
2:36:03,548 --> 2:36:05,516
What will you do?.

1492
2:36:05,884 --> 2:36:08,853
Ever tell what I'll
do and how I'll do,...

1493
2:36:08,920 --> 2:36:10,854
... you'll know when it happen.

1494
2:36:11,223 --> 2:36:14,852
If a single man comes and do
riots in the minister's house,...

1495
2:36:14,926 --> 2:36:16,860
... you'll keep quiet?.

1496
2:36:17,562 --> 2:36:19,530
Beat and chase him out.

1497
2:36:19,731 --> 2:36:23,030
Yes, I'm a single man.
But to give their life to...

1498
2:36:23,101 --> 2:36:26,036
this single man,...... just peep
and see how many are there.

1499
2:37:12,117 --> 2:37:14,244
Hey, how so much of crowd
come into the city?.

1500
2:37:14,352 --> 2:37:17,253
They forcibly entered as farmers.

1501
2:37:18,623 --> 2:37:22,081
See the Padayappa's army.
This is only a trailer.

1502
2:37:22,961 --> 2:37:24,929
You've not seen the main picture.

1503
2:37:24,996 --> 2:37:26,930
If you see it, you'll be shaken.

1504
2:37:27,632 --> 2:37:31,932
You have political influence.
I have people's influence.

1505
2:37:32,971 --> 2:37:36,270
You live on police's power.
I live on people's power.

1506
2:37:36,975 --> 2:37:41,605
Infront of this power,
your power is nothing.

1507
2:37:42,147 --> 2:37:44,274
Let us see if your power is
strong or mine is strong.

1508
2:37:44,649 --> 2:37:46,617
What are you looking,
shoot everybody.

1509
2:37:47,319 --> 2:37:49,947
How many will you shoot
how many will you shoot.

1510
2:37:50,155 --> 2:37:52,350
See how many police do
you have, how many guns...

1511
2:37:52,424 --> 2:37:55,359
...and how many bullets in it.
How many people can you shoot?.

1512
2:37:55,994 --> 2:37:57,962
Do a small calculation and see.

1513
2:37:58,063 --> 2:38:01,362
If you shoot some also,
the others will smash you.

1514
2:38:02,167 --> 2:38:05,295
Come to our side,
or else you'll also die.

1515
2:38:05,670 --> 2:38:07,638
I won't mind that you
are my father-in-law.

1516
2:38:07,839 --> 2:38:09,966
I'll die peacefully by being
a slipper to this man...

1517
2:38:10,041 --> 2:38:12,134
... rather than being a
father-in-law to a man like you.

1518
2:38:12,210 --> 2:38:14,144
Life will go at anytime.

1519
2:38:14,346 --> 2:38:16,314
Let it go after uniting
such a good pair.

1520
2:38:16,681 --> 2:38:18,649
Shoot me!

1521
2:38:19,017 --> 2:38:20,985
Come on lG sir,
give the shooting order.

1522
2:38:21,186 --> 2:38:23,154
If you shoot four people,
others will run.

1523
2:38:24,022 --> 2:38:26,991
Hey, those who run and jump
are on your side, politics.

1524
2:38:27,192 --> 2:38:29,319
Those on this side
are faithful ones.

1525
2:38:29,694 --> 2:38:32,162
If Padayappa says a word,
we won't shout,...

1526
2:38:32,230 --> 2:38:34,164
... but tear you into piece.

1527
2:38:34,699 --> 2:38:36,667
Don't try to test our man.

1528
2:38:36,868 --> 2:38:39,393
If you try it, we will do anything.
What do you say?.

1529
2:38:42,374 --> 2:38:45,343
What are you waiting for?.
It's an order!

1530
2:38:48,046 --> 2:38:50,014
Sir, why do you think
it is so simple.

1531
2:38:52,050 --> 2:38:54,018
See there.
Already the press people are writing...

1532
2:38:54,085 --> 2:38:56,019
... about what's happening here.

1533
2:38:56,087 --> 2:38:58,021
Onething if you wish, I can only
stop them from getting inside...

1534
2:38:58,089 --> 2:39:00,353
... and secure you, that's all.

1535
2:39:00,725 --> 2:39:02,693
If something happens tomorrow,
I can't answer CM, sir.

1536
2:39:03,228 --> 2:39:07,187
Try to convince your son
and get him married.

1537
2:39:07,399 --> 2:39:09,367
What trying to convince him?.

1538
2:39:09,734 --> 2:39:13,363
If the groom is not interested
how will you get him married.

1539
2:39:13,738 --> 2:39:16,366
Have we come to watch it
and give Rs.5 and Rs. 10 as gift.

1540
2:39:16,741 --> 2:39:18,709
We are silent because
you are a police...

1541
2:39:18,777 --> 2:39:20,711
...otherwise we would
have torn you into pieces.

1542
2:39:22,080 --> 2:39:24,048
Tell them brother.
My brother's smile is more than enough.

1543
2:39:24,115 --> 2:39:25,707
Silently send the groom.

1544
2:39:26,151 --> 2:39:28,381
The groom, brother-in-law,
father-in-law are against you.

1545
2:39:28,453 --> 2:39:30,387
This is your family problem, sir.

1546
2:39:31,089 --> 2:39:33,057
Don't make it a
politics sir, please.

1547
2:39:37,095 --> 2:39:39,461
Mr. Padayappa, there
should be no problem here.

1548
2:39:40,098 --> 2:39:42,066
If the groom agrees,
you can take him with you.

1549
2:39:42,267 --> 2:39:47,466
- Do you wish to go with him?.
- Yes.

1550
2:39:56,114 --> 2:39:58,082
This is POLlCE.

1551
2:40:01,286 --> 2:40:04,414
You would now remember the
drama you staged by fooling...

1552
2:40:04,489 --> 2:40:06,423
... and stopping my
daughter's wedding.

1553
2:40:07,792 --> 2:40:12,252
Once you won.
Good. I woke up.

1554
2:40:13,131 --> 2:40:18,262
Now you would have understood
my way is a unique way.

1555
2:41:00,845 --> 2:41:03,143
Tell all our partymen
and blackcats...

1556
2:41:03,214 --> 2:41:07,810
... that my son's funeral might
take place but not this wedding.

1557
2:41:10,855 --> 2:41:12,823
I'm also coming.
Take the car.

1558
2:41:35,547 --> 2:41:37,515
Hey, cut to the left.

1559
2:41:42,887 --> 2:41:44,855
Put the brake and lift to the left.

1560
2:41:55,233 --> 2:41:57,531
Then, what hobbies.

1561
2:41:58,903 --> 2:42:00,871
Sports uncle.

1562
2:42:11,249 --> 2:42:13,217
What game do you like?.

1563
2:42:13,418 --> 2:42:19,618
Cricket...then... hockey,
then... batmintion, tennis uncle...

1564
2:42:23,261 --> 2:42:26,560
I like football See
how it is flying.

1565
2:42:53,291 --> 2:42:55,259
We can't sir.
Come back!

1566
2:43:02,467 --> 2:43:04,662
You lived in city.
Will you like villages.

1567
2:43:05,703 --> 2:43:07,671
Wherever Anitha is,
I like it uncle.

1568
2:43:09,974 --> 2:43:11,942
Hey, there is a pit.
Put the brake and lift.

1569
2:43:16,481 --> 2:43:18,449
He escaped!

1570
2:44:09,701 --> 2:44:11,669
- He escaped from us also, over.
- Go fast!

1571
2:44:12,537 --> 2:44:14,505
See he is coming, hit his car.

1572
2:44:40,565 --> 2:44:43,534
No you are the groom.
Why you go to this rowdies.

1573
2:44:43,601 --> 2:44:45,535
You sit.
I'll tackle them.

1574
2:44:45,737 --> 2:44:48,706
- I've mastered this art.
- No, uncle you are aged.

1575
2:44:50,074 --> 2:44:53,703
Am I you sit inside
and watch my age.

1576
2:44:53,778 --> 2:44:55,712
Sit son-in-law!

1577
2:46:35,680 --> 2:46:37,648
You are not aged.

1578
2:48:23,788 --> 2:48:25,585
A lady is coming with a gun.
What are you looking at?.

1579
2:48:25,656 --> 2:48:27,248
Come all of you.

1580
2:48:33,631 --> 2:48:36,930
Whatever happens here, nobody
should move from their place.

1581
2:50:06,123 --> 2:50:08,091
Forgive me Padayappa.

1582
2:50:08,726 --> 2:50:12,093
No I'm worthless even
to say your name.

1583
2:50:13,397 --> 2:50:15,865
Since I couldn't possess you...

1584
2:50:15,933 --> 2:50:17,867
... I tried to ruin
you and your family.

1585
2:50:18,903 --> 2:50:20,871
But I failed.

1586
2:50:20,938 --> 2:50:24,874
Even now, I tried to kill
you infront of your eyes.

1587
2:50:24,942 --> 2:50:27,103
Still you tried to save me.

1588
2:50:28,746 --> 2:50:31,715
So you are not a human,
you are a God.

1589
2:50:39,757 --> 2:50:43,056
You thought I would say that.
Never.

1590
2:50:44,762 --> 2:50:46,730
I'm not an ordinary woman.

1591
2:50:48,766 --> 2:50:52,896
This anger will not
end in eighteen,...

1592
2:50:52,970 --> 2:50:54,904
... twenty years not
till the end of life...

1593
2:50:54,972 --> 2:50:56,906
... not even if my life ends.

1594
2:50:57,441 --> 2:51:02,071
I'm not servant Vasundra to
live with a life you gave me.

1595
2:51:12,790 --> 2:51:15,418
Hey, you won in this birth.

1596
2:51:16,794 --> 2:51:19,763
If there is a rebirth,...

1597
2:51:20,464 --> 2:51:25,424
... this Neelambari will
definitely take revenge on you.

1598
2:51:40,818 --> 2:51:43,787
Though how many times
you take rebirth,...

1599
2:51:43,854 --> 2:51:48,791
... a greedy man and a loud
woman have never been happy...

1600
2:51:48,859 --> 2:51:51,123
...there is no such history.

1601
2:51:52,163 --> 2:51:54,131
You didn't live happily
when you were alive.

1602
2:51:55,166 --> 2:51:57,134
Atleast let your soul rest in peace.

1603
2:51:59,170 --> 2:52:01,138
God.

1604
2:52:10,848 --> 2:52:13,476
There are thousands
of obstacles in life.

1605
2:52:13,851 --> 2:52:16,820
Obstacles are your stepping stone.

1606
2:52:16,887 --> 2:52:20,823
There are thousands
of obstacles in life.

1607
2:52:20,891 --> 2:52:24,987
Obstacles are your stepping stone.

